  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in fact, any schooling that I have, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you might say high school, regular high school curriculum, stems from those days, because in those days when I went to school, I went in a very serious manner, because not only were my parents sacrificing a great deal, but we were also taking a chance with our lives.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So this was serious business.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was during the day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was during the day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Serious business.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I applied myself with all the strength that I had.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was never a good student before.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Before the war, I was a very poor student.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I could never apply myself to my studies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But during the war, I started to apply myself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, I found that I have an ability to do this and that and the other.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and at- at- a  lot of times, Miss Sobol would call on me to give answers to questions that nobody else knew, and I somehow did.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was a period of my time when I learned a great deal.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With Miss Sobol, I took German, I took French, and I took English.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and these-- and I also took Latin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all these languages came in very handy in my later years as I needed them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that was my own part, you know, but that had nothing to with my parents [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you know, things got tougher and tougher.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as I said, these Germans, his bosses, dropped the association.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they would no longer have anything to do with us, because, you know, they thought that Hitler has got it, that that's going to be it.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
